                            <comment id="12950537" author="davsclaus" created="Thu, 29 Jan 2009 12:02:12 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Trev, could you paste the stacktrace please.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;FactoryFinder delegates its classloading to ObjectHelper.loadClass and it looks like it handles the null. So a stacktrace is needed.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12950559" author="trev" created="Fri, 30 Jan 2009 04:36:06 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;ObjectHelper.loadClass returns a null, and eventually FactoryFinder.findClass passes that null to ConcurrentHashMap.put, which causes the NPE.  Stacktrace attached.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12950553" author="davsclaus" created="Fri, 30 Jan 2009 07:29:10 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Trev, thanks for the stacktrace.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I am currently improving Camel to be able to handle the nulls.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
